![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578167962062-M8EYWRJDHTN551FYERKE/image-asset.jpeg)

The SNAP heard around the world has led to the cancellation of Luke Cage and Iron Fist, but the Devil of Hell's Kitchen still has has work to be done. Join us as we talk all things Daredevil Season 3, catch up with our boy Matt Murdock, try to rank each season of the show, and get into deep philosophical discussion about its Catholic themes, comic book inspiration, and character development in what some might say is our best show yet! Plus you can hear listener's opinion on the season with a BRAND NEW set of feedback from the member of the Clique! 

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

